  "text": "Where are these three energies now? I am Ra. These entities are in the dimension known to you as a fourth. Therefore, the space time continua are not compatible and approximation of the space-time locus of each would knit no actual understanding. Each chose a fourth density planet which was dedicated to the pursuit of the understanding of the law of one through service to self, one in what you know as the Orion group, one in what you know as Cassiopia, one in what you know as Southern Cross. However these loci are not satisfactory. We do not have vocabulary for the geometric calculations necessary for transfer of this understanding to you.",
